## Problem
Grok credits period type can be monthly/daily (`periodLabel`), but `periodMs` is hard-coded to `MS_7D`. Time-percent / pace for non-weekly credit periods will be wrong.

## Location
contents/ui/js/QuotaParsers.js:2059-2077

## Suggested fix
Derive `periodMs` from period type (or from start/end timestamps when present).

## Source
Review ff0a2eec Issue 14 (suggestion)